1
00:00:38,420 --> 00:00:41,060
=How to Train Your Killer=

2
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:43,900
=Episode 29=

3
00:00:49,030 --> 00:00:50,030
Who is it?

4
00:00:52,710 --> 00:00:53,560
Shiyi?

5
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,840
What happened to you?

6
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:00,840
Come on. Come in quickly.

7
00:01:10,350 --> 00:01:11,190
Done.

8
00:01:14,790 --> 00:01:16,560
The wounds on your body
can be healed easily.

9
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:18,400
But the ones in your heart

10
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,590
are harder to mend, you know.

11
00:01:21,230 --> 00:01:22,310
Oh, right.

12
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,840
That young lady

13
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,040
is really quite considerate;

14
00:01:33,430 --> 00:01:35,350
she even asked someone
to send some things over,

15
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:37,590
saying they were to make it up to you.

16
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:39,150
But I think

17
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,710
you don't need those worldly trinkets.

18
00:01:46,230 --> 00:01:47,590
That's more like it.

19
00:01:47,950 --> 00:01:49,510
How could a soulmate

20
00:01:49,510 --> 00:01:51,760
compare to a chest
full of gold and jewels?

21
00:01:58,150 --> 00:01:59,280
Beyond any cure.

22
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:00,950
Thick as a brick.

23
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:01,960
Forget it.

24
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,040
They're all mine.

25
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:14,870
I didn't expect

26
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:20,000
she actually returned this rouge to me.

27
00:02:24,050 --> 00:02:25,090
Reporting to you, My Lord.

28
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,120
Minister Gu...

29
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:27,960
Speak.

30
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,710
There's no property left
under Gu Pingzhang's name.

31
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:34,000
How could a treacherous villain
plotting rebellion

32
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:37,280
possess only these few assets
in his household?

33
00:02:38,310 --> 00:02:40,680
Finding it would benefit
both you and me.

34
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:43,120
That Gu scoundrel is cunning indeed.

35
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:45,430
He must have secretly moved
all his possessions.

36
00:02:46,230 --> 00:02:48,240
Yet His Majesty forbids any action
against him.

37
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:50,520
In this world,

38
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:52,750
there are many ways

39
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:55,870
to force someone to tell the truth

40
00:02:56,310 --> 00:02:58,030
without harming their life.

41
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:00,400
You're a clever one.

42
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,080
You know what to do

43
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,280
without me teaching you, right?

44
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,640
Yes.

45
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,840
I understand.

46
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:08,030
Move out.

47
00:03:38,300 --> 00:03:40,660
(Benevolent and Compassionate)
All traitors of the Pavilion

48
00:03:40,660 --> 00:03:41,800
were put to death.

49
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:44,240
Following the doctrine
of striking

50
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,520
rather than sparing,

51
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:47,190
not a single one was left behind.

52
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,120
Eunuch Leng,

53
00:03:51,590 --> 00:03:52,520
do you think

54
00:03:53,310 --> 00:03:55,120
if I've been too ruthless?

55
00:03:56,190 --> 00:03:59,080
You firm resolve is a virtue.

56
00:03:59,430 --> 00:04:02,030
The peace of the realm
concerns the lives of all subjects.

57
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,470
A little bloodshed may secure...

58
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:05,840
That's not what I asked.

59
00:04:08,150 --> 00:04:09,870
I was asking about Qingyao.

60
00:04:10,910 --> 00:04:11,910
How is she now?

61
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,120
Her Highness...

62
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:21,050
She still refuses to return
to the Palace,

63
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:23,440
and only wishes to stay
at the Crown Prince's Residence.

64
00:04:26,210 --> 00:04:27,500
Go with me to the Eastern Palace.

65
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:29,230
Yes, Your Majesty.

66
00:04:38,430 --> 00:04:39,360
Qingyao...

67
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:49,950
Enough.

68
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,080
Don't be upset.

69
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,560
Haven't you always wanted a fine sword?

70
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,950
This one, the Spike,

71
00:04:56,950 --> 00:04:58,600
is the finest treasure in my collection.

72
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,270
Though I'm reluctant,

73
00:05:02,300 --> 00:05:03,430
I will still give it to you.

74
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:06,840
Thanks.

75
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,070
Although this one

76
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:11,800
is not as good as the Frostfree
from the Sky Pavilion,

77
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,310
it is still my favorite.

78
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,160
Treat it well.

79
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,830
That's enough.

80
00:05:21,310 --> 00:05:22,050
You're a grown man,

81
00:05:22,060 --> 00:05:23,340
always clutching that rouge box,

82
00:05:23,340 --> 00:05:24,340
what does that look like?

83
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,830
Give it back to me.

84
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:36,070
She's just a young lady.

85
00:05:37,630 --> 00:05:39,360
Enchanting flowers
can dazzle one's eyes.

86
00:05:39,630 --> 00:05:41,390
I've been single since the day
I was born.

87
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,310
I've been just fine.

88
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,120
You don't understand.

89
00:05:48,870 --> 00:05:50,040
I'm not like you.

90
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,080
Not like me?

91
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:54,100
What's so different about us?

92
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:57,950
We're both destined
to walk this world alone.

93
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,560
No.

94
00:06:02,310 --> 00:06:03,830
Ever since I met Qingyao,

95
00:06:06,300 --> 00:06:08,380
it was the first time
I had something to hold on to,

96
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:11,630
someone to care about,

97
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:13,800
someone I wanted to protect.

98
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:15,750
Shouldn't you be happy for me?

99
00:06:20,390 --> 00:06:21,360
I know.

100
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,680
She must've been forced
by that vile emperor.

101
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,520
Enough.

102
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,510
That story might fool me,

103
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,720
but don't lie to yourself.

104
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,440
That woman

105
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,310
has never liked you.

106
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,820
One is the emperor,

107
00:06:35,900 --> 00:06:36,920
and you're just a killer.

108
00:06:37,250 --> 00:06:39,070
If it were me,
I'd choose the emperor too.

109
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,600
You,

110
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,720
you never stood a chance.

111
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,630
Do you understand?

112
00:06:49,070 --> 00:06:49,910
No, that's not it.

113
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,000
It's not like that.

114
00:06:59,510 --> 00:07:00,680
It's really not like that.

115
00:07:05,270 --> 00:07:06,110
Your Highness,

116
00:07:06,270 --> 00:07:08,190
you haven't eaten all day.

117
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,280
If this continues,

118
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,690
your health will surely suffer.

119
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,640
Ling,

120
00:07:13,520 --> 00:07:14,730
I want to be alone for a while.

121
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,880
Didn't I already say

122
00:07:35,310 --> 00:07:36,870
I don't want anyone disturbing me?

123
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:40,270
Qingyao, do you not even wish to see me?

124
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:45,590
Your Majesty.

125
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:47,760
Qingyao.

126
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:48,790
Sit.

127
00:07:54,700 --> 00:07:55,900
You envy the martial world,

128
00:07:55,900 --> 00:07:57,690
because you are bound
to the Imperial Court.

129
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,310
It lacks novelty.

130
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:01,560
Once I name you Empress,

131
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,720
we'll have ample time
to travel the land together.

132
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:06,160
I don't wish to go anywhere.

133
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:08,110
I only wish

134
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,480
to stay at the residence.

135
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:16,160
At least you must eat.

136
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:23,430
I have no appetite.

137
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,950
Even if not for yourself,

138
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,750
think of the child you carry.

139
00:08:30,730 --> 00:08:31,870
The night wind is so chilly,

140
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,390
what if something happens?

141
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:41,030
Gu Qingyao is now pregnant.

142
00:08:41,750 --> 00:08:42,670
What?

143
00:08:42,670 --> 00:08:43,840
Is that true?

144
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,960
It is said

145
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:53,750
that a celestial stone
fell beyond the frontier,

146
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:56,150
imbued with the power of thunder.

147
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,840
You understand the pros and cons

148
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,240
better than I do.

149
00:09:05,790 --> 00:09:06,630
Besides,

150
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,630
I do care for you too.

151
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:16,470
Qingyao,

152
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:18,270
what are you doing?

153
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,840
Don't tell me this is for that assassin.

154
00:09:25,150 --> 00:09:26,510
Stop pretending.

155
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,720
You're not Ling Yu at all.

156
00:09:32,030 --> 00:09:33,510
What nonsense are you spouting?

157
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:36,840
I never told Ling Yu

158
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,790
about my pregnancy.

159
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:41,750
Only my father's people know.

160
00:09:44,790 --> 00:09:45,960
You are Wu Yun.

161
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:47,590
Am I right?

162
00:09:55,510 --> 00:09:57,120
I really underestimated you.

163
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,510
But,

164
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,320
how did you manage it?

165
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:05,840
It was Leng Wuchang.

166
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,080
You're quite sharp.

167
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:10,240
If not for Leng Wuchang,

168
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:12,670
I could never have approached
the emperor.

169
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:03,270
So,

170
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:05,960
it was your doing

171
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,480
that Shiyi and I swapped bodies.

172
00:11:08,750 --> 00:11:09,590
That's right.

173
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,960
The power of thunder and lightning,

174
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:13,060
and the art of water fusion,

175
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:15,230
I didn't expect that you would,
by sheer accident,

176
00:11:15,230 --> 00:11:16,650
unravel the body-swapping technique.

177
00:11:16,790 --> 00:11:18,360
It's not just within the Residence,

178
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:21,840
even the Wind and Rain Pavilion
holds a celestial stone.

179
00:11:22,270 --> 00:11:24,550
I originally wanted to swap bodies
with your father.

180
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:25,960
You...!

181
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:26,840
What a pity.

182
00:11:27,510 --> 00:11:29,080
He's too kind and soft‑hearted.

183
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,550
So he lost completely.

184
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:33,150
Luckily, I planned everything
in advance.

185
00:11:33,510 --> 00:11:35,360
No matter which of them wins or loses,

186
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:37,200
I'll always be the one who triumphs.

187
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,390
The former emperor's serious illness

188
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:40,960
was also caused by you.

189
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,350
That foolish woman had long wished

190
00:11:44,350 --> 00:11:46,080
to send that emperor to his grave.

191
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:48,030
I merely whispered a few words,

192
00:11:48,100 --> 00:11:49,550
and she obeyed me without hesitation.

193
00:11:50,630 --> 00:11:51,790
You treacherous wretch!

194
00:11:52,100 --> 00:11:53,590
Your heart is full of wicked schemes.

195
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,700
You even dared to plot
against the emperor.

196
00:11:55,700 --> 00:11:56,510
Bah!

197
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,670
Emperor, Prime Minister, what of them?

198
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:01,200
They're merely shells of power.

199
00:12:01,670 --> 00:12:03,630
They were just born under a lucky star.

200
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,630
Why should they possess everything

201
00:12:05,630 --> 00:12:06,630
so easily?

202
00:12:07,510 --> 00:12:09,790
Some are born to stand above others,

203
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:12,790
while some are fated to be trampled
beneath their feet.

204
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:14,800
Tell me,

205
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:16,910
is there truly such a reason
under heaven?

206
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:21,510
Who are you, really?

207
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,670
Who I once was no longer matters.

208
00:12:25,550 --> 00:12:26,630
What matters is,

209
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:29,750
who I am at this very moment.

210
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:34,390
Stop dreaming.

211
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:37,790
Do you really think
you can deceive everyone

212
00:12:37,790 --> 00:12:39,080
and comfortably be their emperor?

213
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:40,840
I managed to deceive everyone,

214
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:43,130
yet somehow I couldn't hide it from you.

215
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,000
Do you know something?

216
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:49,230
I could have swapped bodies with Ling Yu

217
00:12:49,230 --> 00:12:50,550
as early as ten years ago.

218
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:52,240
Ten years ago?

219
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,390
You were also the cause

220
00:12:57,100 --> 00:12:58,270
of him falling into the water?

221
00:12:58,270 --> 00:12:59,110
That's right.

222
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:01,390
Too bad you disrupted my plan.

223
00:13:01,810 --> 00:13:03,030
Since we've come to this point,

224
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:05,750
I might as well erase your memories,

225
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:08,200
so you can stay peacefully by my side,

226
00:13:08,510 --> 00:13:10,200
and be a carefree empress.

227
00:13:11,510 --> 00:13:12,360
Let go of me.

228
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:13,510
Get away from me.

229
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,750
Then don't blame me.

230
00:13:23,870 --> 00:13:24,790
Shiyi?

231
00:13:37,860 --> 00:13:40,460
♪When a breeze passes by♪

232
00:13:40,980 --> 00:13:44,300
♪The sand and wind burn with longing♪

233
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:46,940
♪Fearless even when thirst
goes unquenched♪

234
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:50,420
♪Like a camel wandering
with eyes closed♪

235
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:53,740
♪When the rain quietly settles♪

236
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:57,060
♪I think of our sorrow yet unknown♪

237
00:13:57,260 --> 00:13:59,980
♪No need to hum the song of the wind♪

238
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:03,780
♪Ignoring the sky darkening before us♪

239
00:14:03,940 --> 00:14:05,540
♪I finally understood that truth♪

240
00:14:05,540 --> 00:14:07,020
♪Yet you have already faded away♪

241
00:14:07,220 --> 00:14:08,860
♪I lose my way in the night♪

242
00:14:08,860 --> 00:14:10,340
♪Not knowing how to still my heart♪

243
00:14:10,340 --> 00:14:12,020
♪Loving you feels like lifetimes apart♪

244
00:14:12,020 --> 00:14:14,980
♪Yet longing flows back into verse♪

245
00:14:15,420 --> 00:14:17,860
♪For you and me to meet again♪

246
00:14:18,300 --> 00:14:21,140
♪We must cross a thousand years
of promises♪

247
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:23,500
♪In the pouring rain♪

248
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:27,860
♪As if you are still by my side♪
